channel.title: 2Speced Client files unpacked
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape,
I was bored one day so I decided to take apart the 2speced client.
The purpose of this is to give the info out so maybe someone would like to spend the time and create a cheat client, but I warn you their UID is like a loop you go through so many files it's going to take hours, weeks, to crack.
Then the packets to login are also ruined as well thanks to bluur.. anyway... I have decided to give you what I've unpacked from their client.
1. The package was a self extracting package so nothing client wise was valuable, the smart thing to do then was install the directory and look into that folder.
2. The client.exe is what your after (it contains all the client class files which I unpacked and left in the folder for your own reference) *MORONS I NEVER SAID RUN IT SO DON'T ACCUSE ME OF SOME BOTNET SHIT OR SOME STUPID VIRUS SHIT YOU FUCKING MORONS*
3. I unpacked the client.exe and receive all the client files and images and all the files for the class files for it to run, bad news, its obfuscated.. plus the classes are renamed most likely using "jshrink"
Here is 2speced client files unpacked, and decompiled by me, and also deobfuscated. Plus the original class files are inside of it too.
I hope you enjoy this release and good luck making custom clients!
Here's a picture of it still packed up...
[img]http://i27.tinypic.com/30nfcwx.jpg[/img]
http://uppit.com/v/SIEX24O1
Thank you,
- Pr0 C0dingz
